      <p>In the information age, this phrase is more relevant than ever. Knowledge isn't just facts ‚Äî it's the ability to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Make informed decisions</li>
        <li>Solve complex problems</li>
        <li>Innovate and create value</li>
        <li>Protect yourself from manipulation</li>
        <li>Empower others and build communities</li>
      </ul>
