        <h3>Societal Impact</h3>
        <p>Access to education and information reduces inequality. Closed knowledge systems (gatekeeping) concentrate power; open ones democratize it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section-card">
        <div class="icon">‚öîÔ∏è</div>
        <h3>In the Age of AI</h3>
        <p>AI changes the game: raw facts are cheap, but knowing <em>how to ask, verify, synthesize, and apply</em> knowledge is the new power skill. Prompting, critical thinking, and domain expertise win.</p>
